@startuml IRouter_swapSingleTokenExactOut
actor User
participant Router
participant Vault
participant Pool
participant Hooks

== Initiation ==
User -> Router: swapSingleTokenExactOut(pool, tokenIn, tokenOut, exactAmountOut, maxAmountIn, deadline, wethIsEth, userData)
note right: User calls Router to swap for an exact amount of tokenOut.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L451-L472
note left: Entry point for exact output swap, validates inputs and prepares params.

== Vault Unlocking ==
Router -> Vault: unlock(params)
note right: Router encodes SwapSingleTokenHookParams and calls Vault.unlock to enter transient state.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L457-L471\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L191-L197
note left: Enables atomic transaction with transient debt management.

== Swap Single Token Hook ==
Vault -> Router: swapSingleTokenHook(params)
note right: Vault executes Router's swapSingleTokenHook.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L581-L602

== Swap Logic ==
Router -> Vault: swap(VaultSwapParams with kind=EXACT_OUT)
note right: Router calls Vault.swap to compute swap amounts for exact output.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L583-L592\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L258-L346

alt shouldCallBeforeSwap == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onBeforeSwap(swapParams, pool)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for pre-swap logic.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L170-L179
    Hooks --> Vault: true
    note right: Hook returns true, signaling success.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L175
end alt

Vault -> Pool: onSwap(swapParams)
note right: Vault calls pool's onSwap to compute input amount for exact output.\n**Code Citation (Pool)**: IBasePool.sol#L67-L70\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L313-L315

alt shouldCallAfterSwap == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onAfterSwap(afterSwapParams)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for post-swap logic.\nMay adjust amountCalculated if enableHookAdjustedAmounts is true.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L192-L215
    Hooks --> Vault: adjustedAmountCalculatedRaw
    note right: Hook returns adjusted amount if applicable.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L210
end alt

Vault --> Router: amountCalculated, amountIn, amountOut

== Token Transfers ==
Router -> Vault: takeTokenIn(sender, tokenIn, amountIn, wethIsEth)
note right: Router handles tokenIn transfer, wrapping ETH to WETH if needed.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L595-L597

Router -> Vault: sendTokenOut(sender, tokenOut, amountOut, wethIsEth)
note right: Router handles tokenOut transfer, unwrapping WETH to ETH if needed.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L598-L600

alt tokenIn == WETH
    Router -> User: return remaining ETH
    note right: If tokenIn is WETH, return any remaining ETH to user.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L601
end alt

== Vault Settlement ==
Vault -> Vault: check _tokenDeltas == 0
note right: Vault ensures all transient debts are settled.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L167-L189

== Router Finalization ==
Router -> User: amountIn
note right: Router returns the amount of tokenIn used in the swap.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L472
note left: Delivers amountIn to user, concluding the operation.

@enduml